name: Laura's Style "Key Largo" earrings
description: Laura's Style "Key Largo" earrings are made with gorgeous faceted blue candy jade, turquoise, and coral stones. Silver plate decorative bead caps and starfish add to the tropical feeling you will acquire every time you wear them. On sterling silver French style lever back ear wires. 1 & 3/4 inches long.

name: Laura's Style "Bahama" earrings
description: Laura's Style "Bahama" earrings are so delicate and charming. They are made of Czech glass iridescent rose beads, and exquisite gold plate bead caps. On gold plate French ear wire. 1 inch long.

name: Laura's Style "Bermuda" earrings
description: Laura's Style "Bermuda" earrings are made with opulent orange Czech glass butterflies, brilliant blue faceted candy jade, and coral stones. On silver plate French ear wire. 1 & 3/4 inches long.

name: Laura's Style " Jamaica" earrings
description: Laura's Style "Jamaica" earrings will sweep you away to another land where the sun warms the sea to the temperature of bath water, and the mild breeze sooths you to sleep. Made of antique bronze filigree findings, Czech glass crystals, and coral stones. On antique bronze French ear wire. 2 & 1/2 inches long from top of ear wire to bottom bead.

name: Laura's Style "Aruba" earrings
description: Laura's Style "Aruba" earrings are super sexy and fun to wear. They scream "take me away!" They were created to be worn in paradise, but they will make you feel as though you are already there. Made of antique bronze and turquoise, and coral stones. On antique bronze French ear wire. 2 & 1/2 inches long from top of ear wire to bottom bead.
